item.title: Run
item.dc:creator: @RandQm RandQm
item.description:
@RandQm wrote:

Looks more like there’s something wrong with your java I guess
maybe try redownloading JDK and JRE,
and restart your computer for the final touch (help with much problems :D)

// this is mine btw,
the line is much longer, maybe thats the problem
so try this one

@echo off title server echo -------------------------------------------------------------------------- echo Loading echo -------------------------------------------------------------------------- java -cp bin;deps/poi.jar;deps/mysql.jar;deps/mina.jar;deps/slf4j.jar;deps/slf4j-nop.jar;deps/jython.jar;log4j-1.2.15.jar;-server -XX:+AggressiveHeap -XX:MaxHeapFreeRatio=90 -XX:MinHeapFreeRatio=90 -XX:+DisableExplicitGC -XX:+RelaxAccessControlCheck -XX:+UseParallelGC -XX:CompileThreshold=1 -XX:ThreadStackSize=128 server.Server pause
